text: Tetramorium simillimum, is a species of ant in the subfamily Myrmicinae. It is a small pale colored widespread species that can be found in almost all the continents. ==References== ==External links== * * at antwiki.org *Animaldiversity.org *Itis.org *Evergreen.edu simillimum Category:Hymenoptera of Asia Category:Insects described in 1851
title: Tetramorium simillimum
